ca.ualberta.moodroid.model

Class MoodModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.moodroid.model.BaseModel
      • ca.ualberta.moodroid.model.MoodModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelInterface

    public class MoodModel
extends BaseModel
    Simple implementation of the mood object. These mood objects currently include our 6 moods:

    Happy Angry Sad Sick Sacred Annoyed

    This class will define the attributes that are associated and carried throughout the entire app for each mood

      • color

        private java.lang.String color
        Hex compatible colour as a string (ie: #ababab). Each color is also thematically associated with each mood, such as the colour red relates with an Angry mood, or blue with a Sad mood
